          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The absolute cross section for production of the",
                "high-energy capture gamma radiation at Ed=0.45 MeV has",
                "been computed from the observed yield of gamma-rays",
                "in two ways:",
                " (1) The first method was based on a comparison with",
                "the yield of gamma-rays from the 7Li(p,gamma) reaction.",
                " The 3He(d,gamma) radiation was assumed to be",
                "isotropic, in accordance with our rough measurements.",
                " On this basis, the total cross section for production",
                "of high energy He3(d,gamma) capture radiation at the",
                "peak of the excitation curve is calculated to",
                "be (0.057+-0.010) mb.",
                " (2) As a check on the first method, a calculation was",
                "also made of the absolute sensitivity of the NaI",
                "crystal for 16.6-MeV gamma-rays. This calculation was",
                "based on the gamma-ray cross sections contained in",
                "ref. (see REL-REF, C.M.Davisson+). A Calculation was",
                "made of the absolute sensitivity of the NaI crystal for",
                "16.6 MeV gamma rays (=0.037 +-0.010 mb)"
              ]
            }
          ],
